I call Rich and Paul.

74
00:04:51.591 --> 00:04:53.761
A night out with those types...

75
00:04:54.594 --> 00:04:56.274
...is a total adventure.

76
00:04:59.966 --> 00:05:03.326
What am I talking about
the Terenzio brothers for

77
