145
00:10:39.539 --> 00:10:41.200
Empty your pockets!

146
00:10:42.108 --> 00:10:45.588
- We just had a little wine. What's the problem?
- You're the problem. you little shit!

147
00:10:45.712 --> 00:10:48.579
Just lighten up. Mooney.
Just lighten up.

148
