157
00:11:14.007 --> 00:11:16.387
Tell you what's gonna be history -

158
00:11:17.944 --> 00:11:19.275
These kids.

159
00:11:19.646 --> 00:11:20.914
Now get them in there.

160
00:11:21.014 --> 00:11:23.414
- Get in there!
- Shit.

161
