Enough already with the moons.

170
00:12:11.931 --> 00:12:14.801
Lead the way. Chief Running-At-The-Mouth.

171
00:12:29.849 --> 00:12:31.214
Holy shit!

172
00:12:31.751 --> 00:12:34.988
That's not a shooting star. It looks like a-

173
