177
00:12:44.408 --> 00:12:46.512
Well. weren't we looking for
the shooting star?

178
00:12:46.612 --> 00:12:48.714
Come on. this looks neat.
Let's check this out.

179
00:12:48.814 --> 00:12:49.809
No.

180
00:12:49.909 --> 00:12:51.770
Let's go. I've seen enough.

181
00:12:52.038 --> 00:12:53.437
Come on. Deb.

182
00:12:54.941 --> 00:12:58.231
I want to take a closer look.
You can stay here.

183
00:12:58.478 --> 00:12:59.478
Alone?

184
00:12:59.579 --> 00:13:02.799
Would you be more scared if
you came with me...

185
00:13:03.116 --> 00:13:04.866
...or if I left you here?

186
00:13:06.219 --> 00:13:09.154
If you left me here. Let's go.

187
00:13:17.830 --> 00:13:19.957
Come on. Come on.

188
00:13:20.066 --> 00:13:22.296
Okay. okay. I'm coming.

189
00:13:31.911 --> 00:13:33.492
Come on. let's check this out.

190
