Of course it is.

243
00:17:29.015 --> 00:17:30.015
Look.

244
00:18:12.871 --> 00:18:14.171
Joe Lombardo!

245
00:18:26.072 --> 00:18:27.369
This way!

246
00:18:46.425 --> 00:18:48.473
